== for windows==

===download===
get git for windows (comes with msys), this will be your command line.
get python2.7 
get []http://blog.teamtreehouse.com/install-node-js-npm-windows nodeJs]
get cyclon 
go to command line
$ npm install cylon cylon-firmata cylon-gpio cylon-i2c

for blink test  
upload examples>firmata>standard onto your arduino  
run code at http://cylonjs.com/documentation/platforms/arduino/